title: Kyushu Basho 2007 - Day 1.avi
description:
Greetings sumo lovers. Here is day one from Fukuoka. Commentary is in japanese, so you can brush up your japanese. If you don&#039;t undestand japanese - tough luck :) No, seriously, I forgot to change audio to english, tommorow will be better.
Anyways, it would seem that Kaio is (still) alive, we&#039;ll see if can kick some sumo ass on the home turf.
Enjoy, and don&#039;t forget: seeding = good karma, not seeding = YOU SUCK!
